    "rich_text_TWtU77": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_F6dWEf": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do i follow up after I spread the word?"
          }
        },
        "text_FDnBME": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Following up with someone after a conversation about God is an intentional way to show how much you—and God—care for them. When the moment feels right, be ready to follow the Holy Spirit into a conversation about God with them, and see if they’re open to talking more. </p>",
            "align_text_block": "left",
            "block_bottom_space": 30
          }
        },
        "text_e6tA7B": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": false,
            "text": "<p>Examples: </p><p>Last month when we talked about faith you mentioned ___.  I wondered if you could share more about why you think that? </p><p>I know I invited you to Christmas church with me last year and it was a busy day- I wanted you to know I’m going the next 3 Sundays and I didn’t know if you had any interest in joining me! </p><p>When you were sharing with me how your life has felt purposeless, it made me think of this daily devotional. I bought you a copy- I would love to go through it with you if you’re interested. </p>",
            "align_text_block": "left",
            "block_bottom_space": 30
          }
        },
        "text_Lkwmf3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Following up is valuable, but the best thing you can do is simply love them well. You are a living example of what a life with Jesus looks like to them, so strive to love them in a way that reflects Jesus. Be intentional about checking in on them, showing them that you care for them if they choose to follow Jesus, or are still uninterested.  </p>",
            "align_text_block": "left",
            "block_bottom_space": 30
          }
        }
      },
